::Aerotaur::
       He listens for a moment and ponders.  "Why not?  We could give the 
base a shot just like anyone else."  He thinks a moment longer and realizes 
the flaw in his logic.  "Except the base has no circulatory fluids to carry 
the vaccine.  Nevermind me I'm going for a walk.  Kup, sir, I'll be around if 
and when I'm needed."  He leaves the now crowded commanders office and 
wanders through the base again.  He turns around one corner and nearly runs 
into Flicker and Nightlight.  He recoils startled.  "Terribly sorry sir, 
ma'am."  He nods his head in apology.

--part1_1c5.66fb8ce.2bafb6cb_boundary
